//
// PF probe — syminfo metadata INJECTION (#19, ENGINE-ONLY)
// Purpose: prove the fundamental-metadata injection path reaches strategy
// behavior. syminfo.shares_outstanding_total has no OHLCV source; the engine
// returns na unless a feed injects a value via strategy_set_syminfo_metadata
// (here through inputs.json::runtime_overrides.syminfo_metadata).
//
// ENGINE-ONLY: this is NOT a TV-parity probe. TV would use the *real*
// fundamental for the charted symbol, which won't match an injected synthetic
// value. Validate the two engine runs below instead (no tv_trades.csv).
//
//@version=6
strategy("syminfo metadata injection", overlay=true, initial_capital=1000000, currency=currency.USD, process_orders_on_close=false, pyramiding=1, default_qty_type=strategy.fixed, default_qty_value=1)

sharesOut = syminfo.shares_outstanding_total

// Gate entries on an injected large-cap threshold. With no injection the
// field is na -> gate is false -> ZERO trades. With injection above the
// threshold -> the dual-MA crossover entries fire.
bigCap = not na(sharesOut) and sharesOut > 1000000000.0

fast = ta.sma(close, 10)
slow = ta.sma(close, 30)

if bigCap and ta.crossover(fast, slow)
    strategy.entry("Long", strategy.long)
if bigCap and ta.crossunder(fast, slow)
    strategy.entry("Short", strategy.short)
